text: Phryneta elobeyana is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Báguena in 1952. It is known from Equatorial Guinea.BioLib.cz - Phryneta elobeyana. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1952
